    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Clocks that designate periods of time audibly by using a striking mechanism on a bell or gong. If the sounds are musical, prefer "chiming clocks."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
